# 6. Iterative vs Recursive

## Iterative

```java
for(int i = 0; i < n; i++) {

}
```

Space = O(1)

---

## Recursive

```java
void fun(int n) {
    if(n == 0)
        return;

    fun(n - 1);
}
```

Space = O(n)

