# 9. Time Complexity vs Space Complexity

| Time Complexity | Space Complexity |
|---------------|----------------|
| Measures execution time | Measures memory usage |
| Affected by loops | Affected by storage |
| O(n²) common in nested loops | O(n²) common in matrices |
| Focuses on speed | Focuses on memory |

---

# Input Space vs Auxiliary Space

| Input Space | Auxiliary Space |
|------------|----------------|
| Stores input | Extra memory |
| Usually unavoidable | Can often be optimized |
| Example: array | Example: temp array |

