# 14. How to Calculate Space Complexity Step-by-Step

## Step 1

Count Input Storage

Example:

```java
int[] arr = new int[n];
```

Input = O(n)

---

## Step 2

Count Extra Variables

```java
int sum = 0;
```

Auxiliary = O(1)

---

## Step 3

Count Extra Arrays

```java
int[] temp = new int[n];
```

Auxiliary = O(n)

---

## Step 4

Check Recursion Depth

```java
fun(n);
```

Depth = n

Auxiliary = O(n)

---

## Formula

Space Complexity

= Input Space + Auxiliary Space

