# Golden Rules

✅ Loops usually affect Time Complexity, not Space Complexity.

✅ Arrays, Lists, Queues, Stacks increase Space Complexity.

✅ Recursion consumes stack memory.

✅ Space Complexity depends on extra memory used.

✅ Always check recursion depth.

✅ Interview Formula:

Space Complexity = Input Space + Auxiliary Space

